<body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <h1>MusicLynx API</h1>
      This is MusicLynx API, a backend for the <a href="https://musiclynx.github.io">MusicLynx</a> music
      discovery platform. It connects to native data stores and remote services that make links between
      music artists including <a href="https://musicbrainz.org" target="_blank">MusicBrainz</a>,
      <a href="https://dbpedia.org" target="_blank">Dbpedia</a>,
      <a href="https://wikidata.org" target="_blank">Wikidata</a>,
      <a href="https://last.fm" target="_blank">LastFM</a>,
      <a href="https://acousticbrainz.org" target="_blank">AcousticBrainz</a>, and others.
      The following modules are accessible: Audio, Artist, Dbpedia, MusicBrainz, MusicLynx, and Sameas.
      <br><br>
      The base URI for the API: <a href="http://musiclynx-api.herokuapp.com">http://musiclynx-api.herokuapp.com</a>
    </p>
